    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "While I'm not completely clear on what causes this issue, you can set that option on two other ways:\r\n\r\n1. via `searchParameters`: https://codesandbox.io/s/j26wz0r6jw\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: 'latency',\r\n  apiKey: '6be0576ff61c053d5f9a3225e2a90f76',\r\n  indexName: 'instant_search',\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    hitsPerPage: 8,\r\n    aroundRadius: 75000,\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. via the `configure` widget: https://codesandbox.io/s/w6pjxo5kjk\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  appId: 'latency',\r\n  apiKey: '6be0576ff61c053d5f9a3225e2a90f76',\r\n  indexName: 'instant_search',\r\n});\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.configure({\r\n    hitsPerPage: 8,\r\n    aroundRadius: 75000,\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2018-09-04T18:04:26Z",
